

d_capacity_5 = {
	is_for_colonizeable = yes
	category = deposit_cat_food
	should_swap_deposit_on_terraforming = no
	drop_weight = {
		weight = 0		
	}  

	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 1 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 0.160 
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 2 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 0.340 
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 3 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 0.540 
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 4 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 0.760 
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 5 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 1.000 
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value = 6 } }
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 1.260 
		planet_emigration_push_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { check_variable = { which = bio_pops value > 6 } }  
		pop_growth_speed_reduction = 1.260 
		planet_emigration_push_add = 1
	}
}

d_robot_capacity_5 = {
	is_for_colonizeable = yes
	category = deposit_cat_food
	should_swap_deposit_on_terraforming = no
	drop_weight = {
		weight = 0		
	}  

	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 5 }
			owner = { 
				is_machine_empire = no 
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed }
			} 
			has_building = building_robot_assembly_plant 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 2 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_capital
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			} 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 3 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 4 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_system_capital 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 5 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 3 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 4 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 3 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 4 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops >= 40
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
}

d_robot_capacity_20 = {

	category = deposit_cat_food
	should_swap_deposit_on_terraforming = no
	drop_weight = {
		weight = 0		
	}  

	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = -1
		job_replicator_maintenance_add = 1
    }
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 }
			owner = { 
				is_machine_empire = no 
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed }
			} 
			has_building = building_robot_assembly_plant 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 10 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_capital
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			} 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 14 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 18 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_system_capital 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 12 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 16 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 14 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 18 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops >= 40
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}

			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 32 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 28 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 36 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops >= 40
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
}

d_robot_capacity_90 = {
	is_for_colonizeable = yes
	category = deposit_cat_food
	should_swap_deposit_on_terraforming = no
	drop_weight = {
		weight = 0		
	}  

	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = {
			has_building = building_robot_assembly_plant			
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 25 } 
			owner = { 
				is_machine_empire = no
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed } 
			} 
		}  
		job_roboticist_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 20 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 40 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = 1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { 
				is_machine_empire = no 
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed }
			} 			
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 75 } 
		}  
		job_roboticist_add = -1
		job_robotic_specialist_add = 1
  	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 60 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = -1
		job_replicator_maintenance_add = 1
    }
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes } 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 80 } 
		}  
		job_replicator_add = -1
		job_replicator_maintenance_add = 1
    }
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 90 }
			owner = { 
				is_machine_empire = no 
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed }
			} 
			has_building = building_robot_assembly_plant 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 45 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_capital
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			} 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 62 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			OR = {
				has_building = building_major_capital 
				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 81 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_system_capital 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 90 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 54 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 72 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 62 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 81 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops >= 40
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
}

d_robot_capacity_110 = {
	is_for_colonizeable = yes
	category = deposit_cat_food
	should_swap_deposit_on_terraforming = no
	drop_weight = {

			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital

			num_pops >= 40

				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
}

				has_building = building_resort_major_capital 
				has_building = building_hab_major_capital 
				has_building = building_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 202 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_mechanical_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_system_capital 
		}
		job_roboticist_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 225 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {

			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 135 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 180 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {

			num_pops >= 40

				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital

		}

			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			NOT = { owner = { has_civic = civic_machine_assimilator } }
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 256 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			has_building = building_machine_assembly_plant
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {
		potential = { 
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 224 }
			exists = owner
			owner = { is_machine_empire = yes }
			num_pops > 10
			OR = {
				has_building = building_machine_capital
				has_building = building_machine_major_capital 
				has_building = building_machine_system_capital 
			}
		}
		job_replicator_add = -1
	}
	triggered_planet_modifier = {

			num_pops >= 40

				is_machine_empire = no 
				is_hive_empire = no
				NOT = { has_policy_flag = robots_outlawed }
			} 			
			check_variable = { which = robot_pops value >= 325 } 
		}  
		job_roboticist_add = -1
		job_robotic_specialist_add = 1
  	}
